                            <comment id="66100" author="linda" created="Mon, 9 Sep 2013 17:51:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Change is available for review in gerrit at &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/7587/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/7587/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="56845" author="adilger" created="Tue, 23 Apr 2013 18:21:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;One caveat still remains on the &quot;lfs df -i&quot; free inodes value shown for the MDT:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If we don&apos;t have as many objects free on the OST as inodes on the MDS, we reduce the total number of free inodes on the MDT to compensate, so that the &quot;inodes in use&quot; number is correct.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;</comment>
